author: Geremie
text:
Day 365 of 365

This year is more than a roller coaster journey for us as a family and for me as an individual, but despite of it all I'm still grateful for everything that I've been through for it mold me to become a better, wiser and a more mature being.

author: Geremie
text: 2018 is about to end, so anything you want to tell me? 😉

author: Geremie
text: God knows how tired my heart is. He knows how I shed tears at night. I just pray for more strength and give me an understanding heart that will continue to care in the midst of pain, anger and frustration.

author: Geremie
text: You can't just give up on someone because the situation's not ideal. Great family aren't great because they have no problems. They are great because everyone cares enough to find a way to make it work and continue to work despite of what has been done.
